---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 pt-20 overflow-hidden bg-brand-bg"
>
  <!-- Technical Grid Background -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03]"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(var(--color-accent) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 80px 80px;"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Radial Glows -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[160px] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-9xl w-full mx-auto relative z-10 px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-12">
      <!-- Badge / Top Label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in">
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-accent"></div>
        <span class="text-xs font-light tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-accent"
          >DISEÑO WEB MODERNO</span
        >
      </div>

      <!-- Main Headline -->
      <h1
        class="text-6xl md:text-[clamp(4.5rem,10vw,12.5rem)] font-bold tracking-[-0.06em] leading-[0.82] text-white animate-fade-in uppercase"
        style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
      >
        <span class="block">Design.</span>
        <span class="block text-accent">Architect.</span>
        <span class="block ml-0 md:ml-32 text-nowrap">Code. Repeat.</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subheadline and CTAs -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end justify-between w-full mt-12 gap-12 animate-fade-in"
        style="animation-delay: 0.2s"
      >
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg text-brand-muted max-w-2xl font-light leading-relaxed"
        >
          Elevamos el estándar de la web moderna. Creamos plataformas digitales
          de alta gama diseñadas para marcas ambiciosas que exigen resultados
          comerciales y excelencia técnica absoluta.
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 w-full md:w-auto"
        >
          <a
            href="#contacto"
            class="group relative w-full sm:w-auto bg-accent text-zinc-950 px-12 py-6 rounded-none text-[13px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-white transition-all duration-500 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(217,255,0,0.15)]"
          >
            <span>Iniciar Proyecto</span>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="18"
              height="18"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="3"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
            >
          </a>

          <a
            href="#portafolio"
            class="group w-full sm:w-auto border border-white/10 px-12 py-6 text-[13px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-all text-center"
          >
            Explorar Casos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Technical Details Decoration -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-12 left-12 hidden lg:flex flex-col gap-2 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-zinc-700 font-display"
  >
    <span>45.4215° N, 75.6972° W</span>
    <span>EST. 2025 / VERSIÓN 0.9.1</span>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute bottom-12 right-12 hidden lg:flex items-center gap-4 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent font-display"
  >
    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse"></div>
    <span>Disponible para proyectos</span>
  </div>
</section>
